# bucketEnd

**Instance Property**

The value of the ending measurement for the bucket.

## Declaration

```swift
var bucketEnd: Measurement<UnitType> { get }
```

## Reading the Data

- **bucketStart**: The value of the starting measurement for the bucket.
- **bucketCount**: An integer representing the number of samples in the bucket.
